## Troubleshooting ping issues

To test VPC peering, I ran the command ping 10.2.13.43

A successful ping test would validate my VPC peering connection because that way I'll be certain that my instance in VPC 1 can connect to my instance in VPC 2

I had to update my second EC2 instance's security group because the ping test had to allow ICMP protocol on IPv4. I added a new rule that allows IPv4 from VPC 1 source

